<L>__{exterior cottonwood 16th fairway day}
<A>__{a leader board reads: simms stadler 10, mickelson mccord 8. a giant gallery lines the fairway and rings the distant green which is fronted by a lake, as: stadler hits a three wood toward the green the ball plunks in the middle of the lake. the gallery groans. stadler just shrugs to simms, as if to say, "i thought i had enough club."}
<C>__{simms}
<D>__{like i told you, it was more'n you had in the bag.}
<C>__{stadler}
