<C>__{tin cup}
<D>__{i could.}
<A>__{simms looks away, at the shot he's facing: a two hundred fifteen yard carry over water. he looks back at tin cup, shaking his head.}
<C>__{simms}
<D>__{i gotta hand it to you, roy. for fifteen holes you've seemed to grasp the concept here: i'm trying to win and your job is to help me.}
<C>__{tin cup}
<D>__{five percent of your earnings does numb the gag reflex.}
